data.description: Welcome to Arizona St, a new home in a well established neighborhood and a home that offers a fully appointed kitchen and large backyard for all your entertainment needs. This move-in ready home has been upgraded throughout and offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Additionally, this home features an open concept kitchen, new cabinetry, and an open living space. This home is ready for the next owner to enjoy for years to come with peace of mind. Did I mention, paid off solar.
